name: Sumwear International Trade Company
overview:
Sumwear International Trade Co.,Ltd was established in 2007 and locates in Ganzhou city, China. We specialize in wholesale and retail China cheap brand sneaker shoes, apparel, handbags and fashion accessories at factory wholesale price.

Our Company specializing in the production of the high quality Products which are the Shoes, Apparel, Handbags,Accessories and more.Whoever you are, and wherever you are, Sumwear offers the best prices. Whether you’re a retailer who refuses to pay the high prices in your country, or a shopper looking to get hold of the latest products, Sumwear.com provides light-speed service and fantastic prices. We buy direct from an ever expanding network of Chinese manufacturers so we can keep costs low while maintaining the highest of standards.

“Quality first, Credit and Service” is our belief, striving for innovation is our goal for evermore.We are looking forward to cooperating with old and new customers. Please contact us at any time for more details.
